<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4596809>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 3. — Protaxodioxylon turolense Vozenin-Serra,n. sp. (holotype MPZ 97/2514):A, transverse section without growth rings; B, tangential section showing uni- or sometimes partly biseriate rays and abundant axial parenchyma; C, tangential view of smooth transverse end wall in axial parenchyma. Scale bars: 100 μm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4596809/files/figure.png" .

